{
  "stem": "9987.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Joshua, was called into the army, because he was in the reserves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister, Berta, was still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was married to Rafal Jakobowitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had two girls-- one, Sonia, and one, Miriam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were approximately nine and six.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we thought that they're going to come back home, that things are going to go back to normal.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Unfortunately, it was not to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were-- we tried to find out wherever the German could, they used to kill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they caught some Jews, if they found them, they used to kill him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Or they used to hurt them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They used to cut their beards, all kinds of things, they used to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And within approximately three weeks-- that's before the end of September-- we found out-- actually, in the middle of September-- we found out that Germany made an-- a treaty with the Soviet Union, that they are going to divide Poland.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Soviet army started to move forward first to the River Sun, which is about 42 kilometers from our town, to the River Bug, which was north of that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the German army started to withdraw to the river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So one side became Germany, German occupation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the other side, Soviet occupation.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
